{"badges":["TM31","TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place butter in mixing bowl and melt <nobr>2 min\/70°C\/speed 2<\/nobr>.","Add milk, water, flour, eggs and salt to mixing bowl and mix <nobr>20 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>. The batter should have the consistency of liquid cream. If it seems too thick, add a little milk. Allow batter to rest for at least 30 minutes before using.","Lightly grease a non-stick frying pan with butter and heat on medium-high. Pour in a small ladle of batter, twirling the pan as you pour to cover base of pan completely. Cook for 2-3 minutes or until edges of crêpe are light golden. Turn crêpe over and cook for a further 1 minute. Transfer to a plate and cover with a tea towel to keep warm. Repeat with remaining batter. Serve warm."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["50 g butter, unsalted, plus extra for frying","500 g milk","200 g water","250 g plain flour","4 eggs","1 pinch salt"]}],"id":"r178863","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-Egf4LaE-mLE\/XZXYpQkzQaI\/AAAAAAAAgAU\/48nMscq4ZMULRZMPsofwP_MTw3YWT2xyQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Qx3k4Yz2wzUsgvxm.png","title":"Crêpes","publishedAt":"2018-04-10T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"7 g","fat":"9 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"21 g","calories":"823 kJ \/ 197 kcal"},"usefulItems":"tea towel, non-stick pan (Ø 22 cm), ladle, hob","hintsAndTricks":["To replace butter with oil, omit <nobr>step 1<\/nobr> and add <nobr>50 g oil<\/nobr> along with all other ingredients in <nobr>step 2.<\/nobr> Use oil instead of butter for frying.","Flavour the crêpes in <nobr>step 2:<\/nobr> add <nobr>40 g vanilla<\/nobr> sugar, <nobr>1 tsp grated<\/nobr> orange zest, or <nobr>80 g sugar<\/nobr> and <nobr>2 tbsp rum.<\/nobr>","Crêpes can be served with sweet or savoury fillings.","Crêpes can be frozen for later use. Place a piece of baking paper or cling film between each crêpe before freezing so they can be easily defrosted. After defrosting, wrap crêpes in aluminium foil and warm in a preheated oven (150°C) for <nobr>5-10 minutes.<\/nobr>"],"basicInfo":["easy","45m","1h 15m","10 pieces"]}